    <h2 class="sect-title">About Somerset </h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Somerset is located in Ward 13 and represented by Somerset is serviced by the
                Somerset-Bridlewood station, the last stop on the Dalhouse line. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Bridlewood is located in Ward 13 and represented by Diane Colley-Urquhart on the Calgary
                City Council. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Provincially, Bridlewood is in the Calgary-Lougheed riding, represented by Dave Rodney and
                federally in the Calgary Southwest riding, the current seat of Prime Minister Stephen Harper.</p>
        </div>
